Simple Audio Streaming.

This script captures audio using PulseAudio and encoding stream using Vorbis,
Sending the result to a IceCast Server via Shout2Cast.

Requires module Gstreamer http://search.cpan.org/~tsch/GStreamer-0.09/GStreamer.pm
--

Esse script captura o áudio usando PulseAudio e codifica esse fluxo com vorbis,
Enviando o resultado para um servidor Icecast usando Shout2Cast.

Requer módulo Gstreamer http://search.cpan.org/~tsch/GStreamer-0.09/GStreamer.pm
